author: Christian Datoc
title: Ruhle: Trump’s White House Isn’t ‘Sexy’ Enough To Compare To Game Of Thrones [VIDEO]
text:
TOP 5533885 
Stephanie Ruhle joked on MSNBC Wednesday that Donald Trump’s White House staff isn’t “sexy” enough to compare to the cast of HBO’s “Game of Thrones.” 
WATCH: 
“This is another ‘Game of Thrones’ moment,” contributor Charlie Sykes first noted. “You cannot overstate how close Paul Ryan and Reince Priebus are.” 
“We keep making these ‘Game of Thrones’ references,” Ruhle cut in. “I watch that show. Those are really good looking, exciting, sexy people on that show.” 
“It is not at all what the White House looks like. I’m just going to throw that out there. We have to find a different comparison.” 
Howard Dean added he isn’t “touching this one with a ten-foot pole.”
